The Masterplan (1998)  
  The Masterplan  
  
  *This is another one of my favorites by Oasis, truly an epic song and*  
  *another where our lads are accompanied by a string and horn section.*  
  *There's alot of weird chords used in this song, and the chords are sort*  
  *of hard to hear (especially in the intro) because of the string*  
  *section, so keep an open mind when you see this transcription on*  
  *paper, because if you play the song, you'll hear these chords are pretty*  
  *much the right ones. Written next to some of the chords I use for this*  
  *song are the chords listed in the official Oasis B-sides guitar book*  
  *(thanks to Paul Das for providing these) in case you want*  
  *to know what that book has listed. Unfortunately, I don't think the*  
  *transcription found in this book is a very accurate one (as is the case*  
  *with many transcriptions in the "official" Oasis tab books) so you can try*  
  *out these chords if you wish, but you'll most likely agree with me that in*  
  *most cases the "official" book is incorrect.*  
  
  *Chords used:*  
   [EADGBe]  
  ***Am      [x02210]***  
  ***A7sus4***  [x02030] or try [x05430] (official book: ***G/A*** [x05433])*  
  ***Fmaj7/A*** [x03210]               (official book: ***F/A*** [x03211])*  
  ***C/B***    [x2x010]               (official book: ***G/B*** [x20003])*  
  ***C [x32010]***  
  ***D       [xx0232]***  
  ***E [022100]***  
  ***E7 [020100]***  
  ***F [x33211]***  
  ***G [3x0033]***  
  
  *Intro:*  
  *Here's my attempt at the intro. It may not be exactly how Noel's playing*  
  *it, but it sounds almost exactly the same. For a couple of other attempts*  
  *at how to play the intro, see the bottom of this transcription...*  
  *Chords used in intro:*  
  ***Am  [x07500]***  
  ***Am/G#***   [x06500] (official book: ***Am(maj7/G#)***   [4x2210])*  
  ***Am7***     [x05500] (official book: ***Am7/G***       [3x2210])*  
  ***Am/F#*** [x04500]   (official book: ***Am6/F#***       [2x2210])*  
  ***Fmaj7/A*** [x03500] (official book: ***Fmaj7***       [1x2210])*  
  ***Am/D***    [x00500] (official book: ***D***       [xx0232])*  
  ***E7 [020100]***  
  *So here it goes:*  
  ***Am   Am/G#   Am7    Am/F#   Fmaj7/A    Am/D    Am    E7 } repeat***  
